{"tid":1369674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣好驚聽日入元朗會比人打...","createTime":"2019-07-26T18:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T06:36:45.000Z","uid":132287,"like":112,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b22ee3c87efed6a34d7b5c304d4f99152e40c438","tid":1369674,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:12:42.000Z","msg":"但係我仲驚聽日因為唔夠人令到手足再比人打<br />\n唔想再好似721果晚咁嬲到喊 嬲到訓唔著<br />\n所以點驚都好聽日都一定要出黎 <br />\n保護身邊每一個同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d09f1ec33e35a19a19844f216ff2c087a355869","tid":1369674,"uid":258927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:13:02.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山, 做乜都好, 搵咗攻略睇先! <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再on 99 講有事退去寫字樓! </span></span><br />\n元朗有L寫字樓/商場你退!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nif 天水被人圍咗, 無交通工具, 跑online 離開元朗去洪水橋/屯門要行 1.5 至 2 小時! <br />\n即係<span style=\"color: blue;\">2倍老銅出支聯辦既距離</span>!<br />\n<br />\n做乜都好, 睇路呀!!! 唔好去送頭呀!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/EzULh8v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzULh8v.png&h=8cea8ccc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地圖傳送門:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1361703/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1361703/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7d1c0fd92d1c5cc7c80014208ab0874ba014403a","tid":1369674,"uid":264591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:13:32.000Z","msg":"[721回程] Yoho Mall 巴士站<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369632</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8981cbe0716106ab84a2cd1561aa7d86874ae308","tid":1369674,"uid":25172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:13:35.000Z","msg":"偷偷地幫老母開咗AirDrop<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369599</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大家幫老豆老母開airdrop 之後sd長輩圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43717c101ae3dacd76aff682c11dedd7e495265b","tid":1369674,"uid":74888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:13:48.000Z","msg":"聽日大家加油！！！"},{"pid":"d9b490ddb2589a19ffcd775a2fc51ea68c8ea0f6","tid":1369674,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:14:05.000Z","msg":"自己既手足自己救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3243895ceca843f8ffaa58fd4cf8f7f70bc0377b","tid":1369674,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:14:10.000Z","msg":"記得上裝<br />\n俾人打要還拖"},{"pid":"d2c2796622446bb4f35a20affe808ae9b346e17b","tid":1369674,"uid":118120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:14:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武負責保護隊友, 和理非負責做宣傳<br />\n好簡單, 幻想下你參加緊魔戒既遠征隊, </span><br />\n遠征過程係會一直受到敵人攻擊, <br />\n你只要擊退敵人就夠, 佢撤退你唔洗追<br />\n目標係保護遠征隊走到終點, <br />\n而被保護既和理非遇到受襲, 亦應該拎起相機拍片, <br />\n提供自己作為人證, 片段作為物證去支撐勇武護衛團既行為正當性<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">遠征隊少左和理非, 勇武是但一方都一定會滅團</span><br />\n大家每個人都好重要"},{"pid":"8bed1189878745860a46c39dab106bd07ad736a7","tid":1369674,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:16:06.000Z","msg":"要保護所有同路人<br />\n唔會向惡勢力低頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5c783a2b9b280872587c7ed0d319bd0f36ed6f0","tid":1369674,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:17:49.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔係住元朗<br />\n但係我住係香港<br />\n所有既同路人全部都係我屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a28a5e2ca1f46a7382ad6e7bbdf7afdcab99b67","tid":1369674,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:19:42.000Z","msg":"如果我果日在場就好 <br />\n就算還唔到手<br />\n起碼可以幫大家分擔幾棍<br />\n等大家冇咁傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a9b296cffb055873eef8bc1677a35da68a5372","tid":1369674,"uid":161859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:20:49.000Z","msg":"你覺得入元朗比人打好恐怖<br />\n咁你想唔想像到我地依加爭取唔返屬於我地既香港<br />\n以後既香港會變成點？<br />\n我地既自由冇曬<br />\n甚至我地既下一代 同樣比人剝削曬所有野<br />\n<br />\n企最前既人一樣驚，雖然唔應該以暴制暴<br />\n但更加唔應該企定定比人打<br />\n香港政府 警察幫唔到我地<br />\n我地靠自己<br />\n<br />\n香港人一定要加油 撐住"},{"pid":"f7364b888a453358a91733d5c7428c6d66246fea","tid":1369674,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:23:05.000Z","msg":"香港人要贏！<br />\n大家撐多陣 撐多陣就得架啦"},{"pid":"5bd2002a6029eaad76bb2e64853db16143821b0c","tid":1369674,"uid":281463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:24:18.000Z","msg":"明日見，要驚一齊驚<br />\n黑衫"},{"pid":"5396368e6de7b3b9850e7232543e7e1f2587e47a","tid":1369674,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:25:27.000Z","msg":"絕不向警黑低頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f74ece8c218c23de902ab66d338e6792630c4546","tid":1369674,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:26:40.000Z","msg":"我會盡全力保護身邊所有既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a54c50fc2b01e78e60114d400d8f6baa97660c","tid":1369674,"uid":132287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:30:58.000Z","msg":"從未試過咁自豪自己係一個香港人"},{"pid":"c81cae9c9b912c0d63c312c3413a0fd94cd8f786","tid":1369674,"uid":127447,"like